---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Cyber Security Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Comprehensive cyber security services including penetration testing, vulnerability assessment, network security, and compliance in the UAE."
  path="/services/cyber-security/"
  image="/img/og-cyber-security.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="security-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Comprehensive Cyber Security Services</h2>
      <p>
        The UAE is one of the most targeted countries in the world for cyber
        attacks, a direct consequence of its concentration of financial
        institutions, government digital infrastructure, logistics networks, and
        high-value corporate data. Threat actors range from opportunistic
        ransomware groups to state-sponsored actors conducting targeted
        espionage. For businesses operating in the UAE — particularly those in
        free zones handling international transactions, healthcare data, or
        critical infrastructure — cybersecurity is not a compliance checkbox. It
        is a core operational requirement.
      </p>
      <p>
        GeneralSoft delivers cybersecurity services that go beyond one-time
        audits and generic recommendations. We work with organizations to build
        security programs that address their specific threat landscape,
        technology stack, and regulatory environment. This includes UAE-specific
        considerations such as alignment with the National Cybersecurity
        Strategy, compliance with Dubai Electronic Security Center (DESC)
        standards, and sector-specific requirements across banking, healthcare,
        and government-adjacent entities.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our approach is grounded in the principle that security must be built
        into systems from the design stage, not layered on afterward. This is
        especially relevant for businesses building custom software, mobile
        applications, or IoT deployments — all environments where architectural
        security decisions made early have an outsized impact on the risk
        profile of the finished system. We work alongside development teams to
        embed security requirements into the build process itself, reducing the
        cost and effort of remediation compared to fixing vulnerabilities
        discovered after launch.
      </p>
      <p>
        For organizations that already have systems in production, we provide a
        structured security assessment that starts with understanding your
        business context — what data you hold, what your critical systems are,
        and what a breach would actually cost you — before moving to technical
        testing. The output is a prioritized remediation roadmap, not a
        hundred-page report that sits unread on a shelf.
      </p>

      <h3>Security Assessment & Auditing</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Vulnerability Assessment</h4><p>
            Comprehensive scanning and analysis of your systems to identify
            security weaknesses before attackers can exploit them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Penetration Testing</h4><p>
            Ethical hacking services that simulate real-world attacks to test
            your defenses and identify critical vulnerabilities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Security Auditing</h4><p>
            Detailed evaluation of your security policies, procedures, and
            controls to ensure compliance and best practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Risk Assessment</h4><p>
            Identify, analyze, and prioritize security risks to make informed
            decisions about resource allocation and mitigation strategies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Application Security</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Secure Code Review — Static and dynamic analysis to identify security
          flaws in source code
        </li>
        <li>
          Web Application Security Testing — OWASP Top 10 vulnerability testing
          and remediation
        </li>
        <li>
          API Security — Protecting APIs from unauthorized access and data
          breaches
        </li>
        <li>
          Mobile App Security — Comprehensive security testing for iOS and
          Android applications
        </li>
        <li>
          DevSecOps Integration — Embedding security into CI/CD pipeline for
          continuous protection
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Network & Infrastructure Security</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Firewall Management</h4><p>
            Design, implement, and manage next-generation firewalls to control
            network traffic and block threats.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Intrusion Detection & Prevention</h4><p>
            Real-time monitoring and automated response to suspicious network
            activity and potential breaches.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>VPN & Secure Access</h4><p>
            Implement secure remote access solutions with multi-factor
            authentication and encryption.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>DDoS Protection</h4><p>
            Defend against distributed denial-of-service attacks that can
            disrupt your services.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Data Protection & Encryption</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Data Encryption</h4><p>
            Protect sensitive data at rest and in transit with industry-standard
            encryption protocols.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Data Loss Prevention</h4><p>
            Monitor and control data movement to prevent unauthorized data
            exfiltration.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Backup & Disaster Recovery</h4><p>
            Secure backup solutions with disaster recovery planning for business
            continuity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Database Security</h4><p>
            Protect your databases from SQL injection, unauthorized access, and
            data breaches.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Compliance & Governance</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>GDPR Compliance:</strong> Implement controls to protect EU citizen
          data and ensure privacy compliance
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>ISO 27001:</strong> Implement ISMS and support certification
        </li>
        <li>
